text: Saptakoshi Municipality (Nepali: सप्तकोशी नगरपालिका) is located in Saptari District in the Province 2 of Nepal. It was formed in 2014 and then again modified in 2016 occupying current 11 sections (wards) from previous 11 wards. It occupies an area of with a total population of 21,139. == References == Category:Populated places in Saptari District Category:Nepal municipalities established in 2014 Category:Municipalities in Province No. 2 Category:Nepal municipalities established in 2016
